title: These Transformers are TOTAL Alphas! #shorts
description:
Transformers: Rise of the Beasts is now on Digital to watch at home!  ► https://paramnt.us/TransformersRiseOTB

Don’t miss out on the THRILLING, action-packed scenes in Rise of the Beasts. Whether you’re a longtime Transformers fan or a new fan, you will have a great time watching.

But now we have to ask... Autobots are the ULTIMATE Transformers, right? WRONG! In fact, the Maximals in the new Rise of the Beasts show us how strong they really are, and Optimus Prime was RIGHT to recruit them. Here’s exactly what they can do…

This short is sponsored by Paramount.
